
ab shauq se ki jaañ se guzar jaanā chāhiye 
bol ai havā-e-shahr kidhar jaanā chāhiye 
kab tak isī ko āḳhirī manzil kaheñge ham 
kū-e-murād se bhī udhar jaanā chāhiye 
vo vaqt aa gayā hai ki sāhil ko chhoḌ kar 
gahre samundaroñ meñ utar jaanā chāhiye 
ab raftagāñ kī baat nahīñ kārvāñ kī hai 
jis samt bhī ho gard-e-safar jaanā chāhiye 
kuchh to subūt-e-ḳhūn-e-tamannā kahīñ mile 
hai dil tahī to aañkh ko bhar jaanā chāhiye 
yā apnī ḳhvāhishoñ ko muqaddas na jānte 
yā ḳhvāhishoñ ke saath hī mar jaanā chāhiye 